buttonComponents.name: File motion to modify TF
buttonComponents.codeAfter:
IF [Alaskan TF] = true AND [File motion to modify TF] = true
SET [Alaskan motion to modify TF] TO TRUE
END IF


IF [Hawaiian TF] AND [File motion to modify TF] = true
SET [Hawaiian motion to modify TF] TO TRUE
END IF

buttonComponents.name: Change property or debt division TF

buttonComponents.codeAfter:
IF [Alaskan TF] = TRUE AND [Change parenting plan or child support TF] = TRUE
SET [Alaskan change parenting plan TF] TO TRUE
END IF


IF [Hawaiian TF] = TRUE AND [Change parenting plan or child support TF] = TRUE
SET [Hawaiian change parenting plan TF] TO TRUE
END IF
